<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Your PixiCred Statement is Ready</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2c3e50;">Your Statement is Ready</h1>
  <p>Dear Valued Customer,</p>
  <p>
    Your PixiCred statement for the period <strong>{{periodStart}}</strong> to
    <strong>{{periodEnd}}</strong> is now available.
  </p>
  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #666;">Opening Balance</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">${{openingBalance}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #666;">Total Charges</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">${{totalCharges}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #666;">Total Payments</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">${{totalPayments}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #666;">Closing Balance</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>${{closingBalance}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #666;">Minimum Payment Due</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><strong>${{minimumPaymentDue}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; color: #666;">Payment Due Date</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;"><strong>{{dueDate}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>
    Log in to your account at <a href="https://pixicred.com/dashboard">pixicred.com/dashboard</a>
    to view the full statement with transaction details.
  </p>
  <p>Sincerely,<br />The PixiCred Team</p>
</body>
</html>
